netloc (Portable network locality)

The Portable Network Locality  (netloc)  software  provides  network
topology discovery tools,  and an  abstract  representationof  those
networks topologies for a range of network types and configurations.
It is  provided  as a companion  to  the  Portable Hardware Locality
(hwloc) package.

https://www.open-mpi.org/projects/netloc/